<servinfosub id = "AENAP70A1104028003">
<title>
DTC Confirmation Procedure
</title>
<attention1>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Perform road test in a place where there is no traffic to prevent an accident.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Road test should be performed by two persons, a driver and a tester, on a level road.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention1>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
Confirm that the following condition is met in this “DTC Confirmation Procedure”.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Battery voltage &#62; 10.7 V
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention3>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Warm up engine to normal operating temperature.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Drive vehicle at 50 to 80 km/h (31 to 50 mile/h) constantly for 20 min. or more.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Stop vehicle, and run engine at idle speed for 5 min.
</ptxt>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70A1104028004">
<title>
DTC Troubleshooting
</title>
<diag type = "test" id = "AENAP70A1104028005">
<testgroup id = "AENAP70A1104028006">
<question>
Was “Engine and Emission Control System Check” performed?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Go to Step 2.
</ptxt>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Go to 
<intxref refid = "AENAP70A1104001">Engine and Emission Control System Check</intxref>
.
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
<testgroup id = "AENAP70A1104028007">
<title>
DTC Check
</title>
<question>
Is there any DTC(s) other than P0137, P0138 and P0140?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Go to troubleshooting for applicable DTC(s).
</ptxt>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Go to Step 3.
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
<testgroup id = "AENAP70A1104028008">
<title>
HO2S signal circuit and ground circuit check
</title>
<test1>
<ptxt>
When ignition is “OFF”, disconnect “C01” and “E01” connectors of ECM and HO2S connector.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Check for proper terminal connection to “C01” and “E01” connectors and HO2S connector.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
If connections are OK, check the following points.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Resistance of “B2” and “B3” circuits: less than 1 Ω
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Resistance between each of “B2” and “B3” circuits and ground: infinity
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Resistance between “B2” circuit terminal and other terminal at HO2S connector: infinity
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Resistance between “B3” circuit terminal and other terminal at HO2S connector: infinity
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Voltage of “B2” and “B3” circuits: 0 to 1 V (When ignition is “ON”)
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</test1>
<question>
Is check result OK?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Go to Step 4.
</ptxt>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Repair or replace defective wiring harness.
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
<testgroup id = "AENAP70A1104028009">
<title>
Exhaust system and air intake system check
</title>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Check exhaust system and air intake system for clogging or leakage.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<question>
Is check result OK?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Go to Step 5.
</ptxt>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Repair or replace defective part.
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
<testgroup id = "AENAP70A1104028010">
<title>
HO2S heater circuit check
</title>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Check HO2S heater circuits according to Steps 2 through 3 under 
<intxref refid = "AENAP70A1104016">DTC P0036 / P0037 / P0038</intxref>
.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<question>
Is check result OK?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Go to Step 6.
</ptxt>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Repair or replace defective part.
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
<testgroup id = "AENAP70A1104028011">
<title>
Fuel injectors and its circuit check
</title>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Check fuel injector circuit. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A1704003"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Check fuel injectors. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A1706009"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</test1>
<question>
Is check result OK?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Go to Step 7.
</ptxt>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Faulty injection(s) or its circuit.
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
<testgroup id = "AENAP70A1104028012">
<title>
DTC recheck
</title>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Replace HO2S. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A1306015"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Perform DTC confirmation procedure to check for DTCs.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<question>
Is DTC P0137, P0138 or P0140 still detected?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Replace ECM and recheck DTC. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A1306001"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
End.
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
</diag>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
</section></manual></suzuki>
